description:
Change of use of corner block from 3005sq m Class B1
office and 285sq m Class B1c workshop to 37 additional
residential flats on ground to sixth floors  as a
variation to the planning permission dated 16.11.93
(Reg No: 9300159/R4) for redevelopment of the site
for residential  retail  office  workshop  hotel
health club and ancillary purposes.
as shown on drawing no 0011/PL/02E 3C 4F 5E 16D 17C
20B 21C 22D 24C as revised on 05.04.94  18.04.94
decision_conditions:
Condition : 1 - The number of car spaces as shown on the 2 basement level
    plans hereby approved shall be no more than 148 in total
    and shall be allocated at the following maximum levels for
    the various land uses and permanently retained as such:
    Health Club 2 spaces  Hotel & Conference room 30 spaces
    Retail 7 spaces  Residential 109 spaces

Condition : 2 - To ensure that the car parking spaces are used in
    accordance with the intentions of the proposed scheme and
    are not used for unauthorised purposes.
